See `AGENTS.md` at the repo root for the full guide.

Key rules:
- NEVER edit `src/components/ui/` or `src/components/primitives/` — managed by Viana Kit CLI
- Build product UI in `src/components/blocks/` using `App*` primitives
- Import from `@/components/primitives/*` only — never from `@/components/ui/*`
- Styling: Tailwind CSS v4 utility classes + semantic tokens only. No inline styles. No hardcoded colors.
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` to merge class names

Full instructions, component list, and templates → `AGENTS.md`
